The Czech Republic then exceeded, for example, the fixed volumes for conserve fungi and therefore threatened a heavy penalty.
The organizers of this investigation found interesting the idea of paying amounts of money to some countries because they don’t have access to the sea and the idea of granting a subsidy to request the grant.
These ideas, however, are not from Brussels but from Prague.
“The fact that we don’t have sea is a disadvantage.
