In large cities, there are multiple-storey shopping centers that almost only sell counterfeits.
However, Pattloch’s cases are different: its mandates charge him to deal with the fact that the Chinese Brand Office officially gives Chinese companies the right to use a name that is already protected in another country.
The Chinese people speak of "Bang Mingpai", a parent brand.
The term is derived from “Bang Dakuan”.
It is with this term that women marry wealthy men.
The Chinese authorities say they have nothing to blame.
